oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Mascot, Knox County, TN, before 1914
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Mascot, Knox County, TN, before 1914. Shows nine people posing on large log, railroad cars in background. Vernon Ed Cole in Center, lying down. Left: W.D. Pettigrew, 2nd from right Katherine Cole, far right, R.A. Jarnigan.
